---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | FastClickTest.com"
  description="Privacy policy for FastClickTest.com. Your click scores are stored locally in your browser only — nothing is sent to our servers. Read how we handle data."
  currentPage="privacy"
>
<div class="page">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Privacy <span class="hi">Policy</span></h1>
    <p>Last updated: January 2025 — We keep it simple and honest.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="seo-content">

    <h2>Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      FastClickTest.com is built with privacy in mind. We collect as little data as possible,
      store nothing personal on our servers, and give you full control over what's saved on your
      own device. Here's exactly what happens with your data.
    </p>

    <h3>1. Your Click Scores</h3>
    <p>
      Your CPS scores, best scores, and session history are stored entirely in your browser's
      <strong>localStorage</strong> — on your own device only. We never transmit this data to
      our servers. You can delete it anytime by clearing your browser's site data for FastClickTest.com.
    </p>

    <h3>2. Analytics</h3>
    <p>
      We use <strong>Google Analytics</strong> to understand how people use the site — page views,
      country of origin, device type, and referral source. All analytics data is anonymized and
      aggregated. It cannot be used to identify individual users.
    </p>

    <h3>3. Advertising</h3>
    <p>
      We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display ads. AdSense may use cookies to show ads
      relevant to your interests based on prior browsing. You can opt out of personalized ads at
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">adssettings.google.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h3>4. Cookies</h3>
    <p>
      We set one first-party cookie to remember your dark/light mode preference. Google Analytics
      and AdSense set their own cookies under Google's privacy policy. You can manage or block
      all cookies through your browser settings at any time.
    </p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>
      You can clear your score history anytime via your browser's localStorage settings.
      You can opt out of Google Analytics using the
      <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GA Opt-out Add-on</a>.
      You can opt out of personalized ads via Google's ad settings. For any other privacy concerns,
      contact us via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
    </p>

    <h3>6. Children's Privacy</h3>
    <p>
      FastClickTest does not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. No account,
      email address, or personal information is required to use any feature of this site.
    </p>

    <h3>7. Third-Party Links</h3>
    <p>
      Our site may link to external websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.
      Review the privacy policy of any third-party site before sharing personal information.
    </p>

    <h3>8. Changes</h3>
    <p>
      We may update this policy occasionally. The date at the top of this page reflects the latest
      revision. Continued use of the site after updates means you accept the revised policy.
    </p>

  </div>

</div>
</Layout>
